							      </table>
							      <div class="remark_footblock">
							      <p ng-hide="docVar.docPrBackPatVO.provisionalList.length <= 0">
							      	<span class="title_text">* Provisional</span>
							      	<span ng-repeat="provision in docVar.docPrBackPatVO.provisionalList"> 
							         <span ng-class="{'font_color_888': true, 'text_divbar': !$last, 'float_l': $last}" ng-bind-html="provision.applNum"></span>
							        </span>
							      </p> 
							      <p ng-hide="docVar.docPrBackPatVO.missingList.length <= 0">
							      	<span class="title_text2">* 미포함 문헌 : <span ng-bind="docVar.docPrBackPatVO.pageCountVO.missingDocCount" ></span>건 (절차상 미공개 문헌, 과거분 문헌, WIPS 보유 데이터 범위에 포함되지 않는 문헌)</span>
